These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, dubstep, indie, rock
1. the fan of jazz is on the left of the fan of rock##1
2. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of indie##1
3. the fan of jazz is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | indie | dubstep | jazz | rock |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, lizard, ferret, dog
1. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the cat is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Pet   | cat | ferret | lizard | dog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, dancing, skydiving, card-games
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby   | skydiving | singing | dancing | card-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, car, taxi, snowmobile
1. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |  2   |    3    |  4  |
| Transport   | taxi | boat | car | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
